Package: debug-assistant
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pyqt5, python3-serial, python3-pyqt5.sip, python3-pyqt5.qtserialport
Description: A debug tool with plugin support
 Debug Assistant is a powerful debugging tool that supports dynamic
 loading of Python plugins. It provides an intuitive interface for managing
 plugins and viewing debug output and logs.
 .
 Main features:
  - Dynamic plugin loading system
  - Plugin management interface
  - Log and debug output windows
  - Extensible plugin architecture
